  <li><strong>Supervised Learning</strong> (i.e. Spam Detection, Image Classification)
<a href="https://postimg.cc/sQyMbq81"><img src="https://i.postimg.cc/bJS1Sj90/4123124123.png" width="700px" title="source: imgur.com" /></a></li>
