<ul>
  <li>Like Alphago, we‚Äôve found roundabout and unlikely ways of achieving our Goal</li>
  <li>The action taken doesn‚Äôt necessarily have to have an obvious / explicit relationship to the Goal</li>
  <li>we might desire riches/money -but why? Maybe natural selection or leads to better health and social status. there are no laws physics which govern riches and gene replication</li>
  <li>it‚Äôs a novel solution to the problem</li>
  <li>AI can also find such strange or unusual ways to achieve a goal</li>
</ul>

